title: The Future of the Swamp
description:
Wendi Nix, Greg McElroy, and Joey Galloway spill breaking news that Florida has paused all football activities, discuss this weekend's Georgia v Alabama matchup and talk about the undervalued Travis Etienne of Clemson.
